(581, 3, '2020-06-09 18:07:03', '2020-06-09 18:07:03', '<b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Hi, my name if </span></b><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">Farren</span></b><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">.  I have had dogs my entire life and after High School new that I wanted to work with them as a vocation, so I began my career path.  I have mentored under Kristi for the past year and a half as I worked on my Veterinary Technician degree.  My ultimate goal is to help the animals by clearly resolving behavioral issues as I help address their health.</span></b><span data-ccp-props=\"{}\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span data-ccp-props=\"{}\"> </span>', 'Farren Flickinger', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'farren-flickinger', '', '', '2020-06-09 18:28:10', '2020-06-09 18:28:10', '', 0, 'http://dogtrainer.canyonbusiness.tech/?post_type=our-teams&#038;p=581', 0, 'our-teams', '', 0),
